14:51.391 --> 14:54.258
Spartacus evades
poor Gaius once again.

14:55.895 --> 14:58.136
I fear your games will suffer
from the Thracian's absence.

14:58.314 --> 15:00.805
Good Mercato
assures me grand spectacle

15:00.983 --> 15:03.395
