to sacrificed his

17:20.206 --> 17:22.663
for something soiled
and ruined.

17:22.833 --> 17:25.210
Spartacus calls for you.

17:47.692 --> 17:49.307
Nasir?

17:50.403 --> 17:52.064
He yet fights.

17:53.990 --> 17:55.480
As do we all.

17:56.534 --> 17:59.071
