to make attempt.

18:28.399 --> 18:31.106
- For good fucking reason.
- Who is more familiar with the arena

18:31.277 --> 18:34.064
than men who have fought
upon its sands?

18:41.495 --> 18:43.360
What are your thoughts?

18:43.539 --> 18:46.121
