serve as message

18:46.292 --> 18:48.123
that Rome
will smother any flame

18:48.294 --> 18:50.159
that burns against its rule.

18:53.132 --> 18:55.623
I would send message
of our own,

18:55.801 --> 18:59.134
one that will ignite the hearts
of all yet enslaved.

19:05.686 --> 19:07.677
( footsteps )

19:16.656 --> 19:20.990
