20:33.107 --> 20:35.723
There is yet much
of the past between us.

20:36.819 --> 20:39.686
Let us see
if there is a future.

20:44.910 --> 20:47.071
( door opens)

20:47.246 --> 20:48.907
Guard: Be quick.

20:54.253 --> 20:56.585
( chuckles )

20:56.756 --> 21:00.089
At last she comes.

21:00.259 --> 21:02.796
