of how you were returned to us

21:33.626 --> 21:35.912
from dark woods for a purpose,

21:36.086 --> 21:38.463
of how the gods
yet have use for you,

21:38.631 --> 21:40.292
as do |.

21:42.760 --> 21:44.250
